{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-02",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_02_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 2 - Death in the Fog",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 6,
  "page_total": 7,
  "page_start_sec": 1216.78,
  "page_end_sec": 1457.0,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.753,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 1216.78,
      "end": 1218.84,
      "text": "His face was stupid in its blankness."
    },
    {
      "start": 1220.192,
      "end": 1221.78,
      "text": "Lieutenant Dundee raised the two bent",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1221.78,
      "end": 1223.88,
      "text": "fingers toward the private detective's chest,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1224.14,
      "end": 1224.92,
      "text": "quickly lowered them,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1225.0,
      "end": 1225.36,
      "text": "and said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1226.16,
      "end": 1228.38,
      "text": "I gave you ten minutes to get to a",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1228.38,
      "end": 1230.02,
      "text": "phone and do your talking to the girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 1230.62,
      "end": 1233.68,
      "text": "I gave you ten to fifteen minutes to get to Thursby's Joint,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1234.3,
      "end": 1235.24,
      "text": "Gary near Leavenworth."
    },
    {
      "start": 1235.66,
      "end": 1237.4,
      "text": "You could do it easy in that time."
    },
    {
      "start": 1237.984,
      "end": 1239.46,
      "text": "And that gives you ten or fifteen"
    },
    {
      "start": 1239.46,
      "end": 1241.696,
      "text": "minutes of waiting before he showed up.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1242.22,
      "end": 1243.88,
      "text": "I knew where he lived,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1244.04,
      "end": 1245.12,
      "text": "Spade asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 1245.984,
      "end": 1248.7,
      "text": "And I knew he hadn't gone straight home after killing Miles.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1249.9,
      "end": 1250.96,
      "text": "You knew what you knew,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1251.936,
      "end": 1252.89,
      "text": "Dundee replied stubbornly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1253.92,
      "end": 1254.92,
      "text": "What time did you get home?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1256.22,
      "end": 1259.5,
      "text": "twenty minutes to four i walked around thinking things over",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1260.1,
      "end": 1265.04,
      "text": "the lieutenant wagged his round head up and down we knew you"
    },
    {
      "start": 1265.04,
      "end": 1268.48,
      "text": "weren't home at three-thirty he said we tried to get you on the"
    },
    {
      "start": 1268.48,
      "end": 1273.5,
      "text": "phone where'd you do your walking outbush street away and back"
    },
    {
      "start": 1274.48,
      "end": 1276.6,
      "text": "\"'Did you see anybody that—'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1276.76,
      "end": 1276.98,
      "text": "\"'No."
    },
    {
      "start": 1277.26,
      "end": 1280.24,
      "text": "No witnesses,' Spade said and laughed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1280.42,
      "end": 1281.4,
      "text": "but pleasantly now."
    },
    {
      "start": 1282.752,
      "end": 1283.18,
      "text": "\"'Sit down,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1283.22,
      "end": 1283.52,
      "text": "Dundee."
    },
    {
      "start": 1284.34,
      "end": 1285.54,
      "text": "You haven't finished your drink.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1286.32,
      "end": 1286.88,
      "text": "Get your glass,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1287.0,
      "end": 1287.36,
      "text": "Tom.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1288.28,
      "end": 1288.7,
      "text": "Tom said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1289.24,
      "end": 1289.6,
      "text": "\"'No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1289.6,
      "end": 1290.08,
      "text": "thanks.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1291.136,
      "end": 1291.84,
      "text": "Dundee sat down,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1291.94,
      "end": 1293.88,
      "text": "but paid no attention to his glass of rum."
    },
    {
      "start": 1295.008,
      "end": 1296.16,
      "text": "Spade filled his own glass,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1296.4,
      "end": 1296.74,
      "text": "drank,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1296.92,
      "end": 1298.54,
      "text": "put the empty glass on the table,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1298.66,
      "end": 1300.66,
      "text": "and resumed his seat on the side of the bed."
    },
    {
      "start": 1302.56,
      "end": 1304.68,
      "text": "\"'I know where I stand now,' he said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1304.84,
      "end": 1307.78,
      "text": "looking with friendly eyes from one police detective to the other."
    },
    {
      "start": 1309.04,
      "end": 1310.66,
      "text": "\"'I'm sorry I got up on my hind legs,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1311.38,
      "end": 1312.64,
      "text": "but you birds made me nervous,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1312.88,
      "end": 1315.1,
      "text": "coming in and trying to put the work on me."
    },
    {
      "start": 1316.22,
      "end": 1317.86,
      "text": "Having Miles knocked off bothered me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1318.4,
      "end": 1320.38,
      "text": "and then you birds cracking foxy."
    },
    {
      "start": 1321.44,
      "end": 1322.18,
      "text": "That's all right now,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.3,
      "end": 1322.5,
      "text": "though,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.54,
      "end": 1324.5,
      "text": "now that I know what you're up to.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1325.54,
      "end": 1325.98,
      "text": "Tom said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1326.816,
      "end": 1327.4,
      "text": "\"'Forget it.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1328.14,
      "end": 1329.14,
      "text": "The lieutenant said nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 1329.34,
      "end": 1330.98,
      "text": "Spade asked,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1331.968,
      "end": 1332.84,
      "text": "\"'Thursby's dead?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1333.9,
      "end": 1335.12,
      "text": "While the lieutenant hesitated,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1335.32,
      "end": 1335.82,
      "text": "Tom said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1336.3,
      "end": 1337.06,
      "text": "\"'Yes.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1338.368,
      "end": 1340.06,
      "text": "Then the lieutenant said angrily,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1340.84,
      "end": 1342.36,
      "text": "\"'And you might just as well know it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1342.38,
      "end": 1343.24,
      "text": "if you don't,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1343.56,
      "end": 1346.02,
      "text": "that he died before he could tell anybody anything.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1347.392,
      "end": 1348.64,
      "text": "Spade was rolling a cigarette.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1349.34,
      "end": 1350.58,
      "text": "He asked without looking up,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1351.5,
      "end": 1352.46,
      "text": "\"'What do you mean by that?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1352.82,
      "end": 1354.34,
      "text": "You think I did know it?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1355.2,
      "end": 1358.2,
      "text": "\"'I meant what I said,' Dundee replied bluntly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1359.328,
      "end": 1360.82,
      "text": "Spade looked up at him and smiled,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1361.08,
      "end": 1363.12,
      "text": "holding the finished cigarette in one hand,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1363.24,
      "end": 1363.64,
      "text": "his lighter"
    },
    {
      "start": 1363.64,
      "end": 1364.14,
      "text": "in the other."
    },
    {
      "start": 1365.72,
      "end": 1367.0,
      "text": "\"'You're not ready to pinch me yet,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1367.06,
      "end": 1367.38,
      "text": "are you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1367.42,
      "end": 1368.54,
      "text": "Dundee?' he asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 1369.44,
      "end": 1370.44,
      "text": "Dundee shook his head no.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1371.58,
      "end": 1372.82,
      "text": "\"'Then,' said Spade,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1372.92,
      "end": 1374.86,
      "text": "\"'there's no particular reason why"
    },
    {
      "start": 1374.86,
      "end": 1376.38,
      "text": "I should give a damn what you think"
    },
    {
      "start": 1376.38,
      "end": 1377.04,
      "text": "is there.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1378.432,
      "end": 1381.48,
      "text": "Dundee looked at Spade with hard green eyes and said nothing.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1382.784,
      "end": 1383.2,
      "text": "Tom said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1383.36,
      "end": 1384.32,
      "text": "\"'Aw,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1384.46,
      "end": 1385.32,
      "text": "be reasonable,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1385.5,
      "end": 1386.02,
      "text": "Sam.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1387.9,
      "end": 1389.18,
      "text": "Thursby put the cigarette in his mouth,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1389.36,
      "end": 1391.2,
      "text": "set fire to it and laughed smoke"
    },
    {
      "start": 1391.32,
      "end": 1391.6,
      "text": "out."
    },
    {
      "start": 1392.672,
      "end": 1393.32,
      "text": "\"'I'll be reasonable,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1393.42,
      "end": 1394.66,
      "text": "Tom,' he promised."
    },
    {
      "start": 1395.488,
      "end": 1396.78,
      "text": "\"'How'd I kill this Thursby?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1397.46,
      "end": 1398.26,
      "text": "I've forgotten.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1399.3,
      "end": 1400.54,
      "text": "Tom grunted disgust.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1400.992,
      "end": 1401.96,
      "text": "Lieutenant Dundee said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1403.18,
      "end": 1404.98,
      "text": "\"'He was shot four times in the back,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1405.08,
      "end": 1407.8,
      "text": "with a .44 or .45 from across the"
    },
    {
      "start": 1407.86,
      "end": 1410.24,
      "text": "street when he started to go into his hotel."
    },
    {
      "start": 1411.36,
      "end": 1412.18,
      "text": "That's the way it figures,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1412.32,
      "end": 1413.536,
      "text": "though nobody saw it.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1414.78,
      "end": 1417.76,
      "text": "\"'And he was wearing a luger in a shoulder holster,' Tom added,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1418.368,
      "end": 1419.66,
      "text": "\"'and it hadn't been fired.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1421.32,
      "end": 1424.1,
      "text": "\"'What do the hotel people know about him?' Spade asked.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1424.77,
      "end": 1425.32,
      "text": "\"'Nothing,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1425.34,
      "end": 1426.7,
      "text": "except that he'd been there a week."
    },
    {
      "start": 1427.46,
      "end": 1428.02,
      "text": "\"'Alone?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1428.16,
      "end": 1428.84,
      "text": "Alone."
    },
    {
      "start": 1430.42,
      "end": 1431.44,
      "text": "\"'What did you find on him,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1431.52,
      "end": 1432.704,
      "text": "or in his room?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1434.016,
      "end": 1435.54,
      "text": "Dundee drew his lips in and asked,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1436.448,
      "end": 1437.91,
      "text": "\"'What did you think we'd find?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1439.04,
      "end": 1441.42,
      "text": "Spade made a careless motion with his limp cigarette.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1442.3,
      "end": 1444.16,
      "text": "Something to tell you who he was,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1444.3,
      "end": 1445.16,
      "text": "what his store was?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1445.94,
      "end": 1446.24,
      "text": "Did you?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1448.0,
      "end": 1449.72,
      "text": "We thought you could tell us that.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1451.552,
      "end": 1454.12,
      "text": "Spade looked at the lieutenant with yellow-gray eyes",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1454.12,
      "end": 1457.0,
      "text": "that held an almost exaggerated amount of candor."
    }
  ]
}